with a little bit of metaphor

00:08:51.300 --> 00:08:53.667
just to kind of get, you know,
your minds in the right places.

00:08:53.667 --> 00:08:56.200
So let's start off
with a pitch black room.

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:58.901
You know, nobody
can see each other.

00:08:58.901 --> 00:09:01.300
You know, no one has any idea
that anyone else is there.

00:09:01.300 --> 00:09:03.567
People are just toiling away
doing their own thing.

00:09:03.567 --> 00:09:05.467
Sounds like a few web sites,

00:09:05.467 --> 00:09:06.934
you know,
that I've visited.

00:09:06.934 --> 00:09:09.367
So if we take that room
and we...

00:09:09.367 --> 00:09:13.100
throw the Google Friend Connect
Members gadget on it,

00:09:13.100 --> 00:09:15.267
we basically are turning
the lights on in that room.

00:09:15.267 --> 00:09:17.100
Right? We're letting people
start to look around,

00:09:17.100 --> 00:09:18.701
see each other.

00:09:18.701 --> 00:09:20.601
You know, they can, you know,
walk up to somebody,

00:09:20.601 --> 00:09:22.434
you know...

00:09:22.434 --> 00:09:24.801
they can't really
do much yet.

00:09:24.801 --> 00:09:27.767
And so that's where you
as, you know, developers

00:09:27.767 --> 00:09:29.868
creating
Google Friend Connect gadgets,

00:09:29.868 --> 00:09:31.234
you really come in,
right?

00:09:31.234 --> 00:09:33.767
So...

00:09:33.767 --> 00:09:35.000
gadgets are really out there

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:36.868
to help members
start to communicate

00:09:36.868 --> 00:09:39.267
with one another
on the site.

00:09:39.267 --> 00:09:41.267
With--without the gadgets
that we create,

00:09:41.267 --> 00:09:43.200
without the gadgets
that you'll create,

00:09:43.200 --> 00:09:45.167
you know, there's not
a whole lot that--

00:09:45.167 --> 00:09:46.534
of functionality
we're offering.

00:09:46.534 --> 00:09:49.868
So on the left
we have our comments gadget,

00:09:49.868 --> 00:09:52.667
which just basically
enables very simple discussion

00:09:52.667 --> 00:09:56.033
between--
between site members.

00:09:56.033 --> 00:09:58.567
On the right, we have
the recommendations gadget,

00:09:58.567 --> 00:10:00.934
and what that does
is it just allows--

00:10:00.934 --> 00:10:04.300
you basically put buttons
around content on your site.

00:10:04.300 --> 00:10:05.501
So, like, in this example,

00:10:05.501 --> 00:10:06.868
the buttons were on photos,

00:10:06.868 --> 00:10:09.067
and members could click on
those recommendation buttons

00:10:09.067 --> 00:10:10.400
to basically
recommend that content

00:10:10.400 --> 00:10:11.868
to other visitors
of the site.

00:10:11.868 --> 00:10:13.534
And then you put
this aggregation gadget,

00:10:13.534 --> 00:10:16.067
like, on your home page
or something like that.

00:10:16.067 --> 00:10:17.334
So that's a gadget
we developed.

00:10:17.334 --> 00:10:19.067
And then in the middle
is a gadget

00:10:19.067 --> 00:10:20.567
developed by
a third-party developer,

00:10:20.567 --> 00:10:22.200
and it's a question
and answers gadget

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:24.601
that basically lets people
ask questions

00:10:24.601 --> 00:10:27.801
and get answers from
other members on the site.

00:10:27.801 --> 00:10:30.100
And so, again,
you know, fundamentally,

00:10:30.100 --> 00:10:32.501
gadgets are enabling people
to communicate

00:10:32.501 --> 00:10:35.434
with one another
on the site.

00:10:35.434 --> 00:10:39.267
So now I want to talk
