00:30:37.501 --> 00:30:38.767
that are going to be exciting

00:30:38.767 --> 00:30:40.567
because I started
thinking about it in this way.

00:30:40.567 --> 00:30:42.267
And things I wouldn't have
normally thought to be,

00:30:42.267 --> 00:30:43.501
"Oh, that should be social,"

00:30:43.501 --> 00:30:45.334
all of sudden, I was like,
"Ah, yeah.

00:30:45.334 --> 00:30:48.634
That could be social and
