00:31:57.968 --> 00:32:01.200
What is the standard?
Where did it come from?

00:32:01.200 --> 00:32:04.167
It came from the idea
that the web is good,

00:32:04.167 --> 00:32:05.868
that social is good,

00:32:05.868 --> 00:32:08.434
but the social web can be
even better than that.

00:32:08.434 --> 00:32:10.767
So where can you
use these APIs?

00:32:10.767 --> 00:32:12.133
You can use these APIs

00:32:12.133 --> 00:32:15.434
